Who are we?
=============

A modern minecraft community for fair PvP gameplay.



- Fair PvP System
- Fully custom developed by our hard working development team
- Dedicated staff team

1) Fair PvP System

   a) Our PvP System has been custom built to be one of most fair PvP Systems you can find on a Minecraft server, 
      it has been hand crafted by our hard working developers who work day and night to keep Nereus up to date.

2) Fully custom server

   a) All of our plugins have been made by our hard working team of developers who will stop at nothing to make the best server they can.

3) Dedicated staff team

   a) Our staff team is one of the best you will find in the Minecraft community, they work very hard to help players and help make games fair.

Please be sure to read our `rules`_.

.. _rules: /docs/rules


